Name: Average time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time elapsed from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time between 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total resolution time of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Reviewer Declined and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to the 'SW-Reviewer Declined' from 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Time to 'SW-Reviewer Declined' since the 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Average time it takes 'SW-Reviewer Declined' after 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Total time it takes the 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to be followed by 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Minimum time for 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to lead to a 'SW-EIC Major Revision' decision
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Average time for 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to impact the 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' stage
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Total time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' in the review process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' before reaching 'SW-EIC Accept'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Time of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' cycle until 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' is performed again
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
